{"tid":1655523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：美國共和黨參議員Josh Hawley「警察極權論」不負責任和不客觀","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T02:56:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":34,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"c3286a2df5ae7f563ba688d3029860a15ac74520","tid":1655523,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"訪港的美國共和黨參議員霍利(Josh Hawley)指香港的制度正在面臨威脅，正在滑向一個警察極權城市。行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">霍利說法毫無根據及不負責任，抱有既定立場，期望外國議員訪港能客觀及全面地觀察香港情況</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠提議成立「暴亂特別法庭」處理與近月示威活動有關的案件。林鄭月娥指出，法治是香港核心價值，當中包括司法獨立，她不會干預或評論任何司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，政府實施《禁蒙面法》其中一個原因，因有大量18歲以下的學生被捕，認為相關法例對未成年人士有阻嚇作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2275805/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2275805%2F&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=8176ecd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2275805/</a>"},{"pid":"f271d3d5319effec2e6d0fae35189c74d748eda7","tid":1655523,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655497</a>"},{"pid":"8cdf09944e39e66b90f823da3cd3adb6f3f4ffde","tid":1655523,"uid":242537,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"即係講撚中撚<br />\n柒婆學撚曬支那維尼熊d玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 